Ray Vitte https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ray_Vitte 0 Raymond "Ray" Vitte (1949-1983) was an American actor who starred mostly in comedy and drama films in the 1970s and early 1980s. He made numerous guest appearances on television shows, and was a cast member of the show Doc in 1976.Vitte was killed in a scuffle with the Los Angeles Police Department in 1983.
